                        </h4>
                        <div className="space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <div className="flex justify-between text-blue-900/70 dark:text-blue-300/70">
                                <span>Monthly Gross</span>
                                <span>₦{finalPay.gross.toLocaleString()}</span>
                            </div>
                            <div className="flex justify-between text-blue-900/70 dark:text-blue-300/70">
